@Name("Item Component - Copy") @Description("Grab a copy of an item component of an item. Any changes made to the copy will not be present on the item.") @Example("set {_component} to the item component copy of (the equippable component of {_item})") @Since("2.13") @RequiredPlugins("Minecraft 1.21.2+") public class ExprItemCompCopy extends ch.njol.skript.expressions.base.SimplePropertyExpression<ComponentWrapper,ComponentWrapper>
